UID:d-f5qHbTOeyVCovLHflMS
SUMMARY:Livestream- Retiring from the UWRP: An Overview
DTSTAMP:20260409T031156Z
DTSTART:20260409T160000Z
DESCRIPTION:Online Thursday\, Apr 9\, 2026\, 9 a.m. - 12 p.m. PDT\n\nWho sh
	ould attend: Faculty\, librarians and professional staff who are participa
	ting in the UW Retirement Plan \\(UWRP\\) and expect to retire within the 
	next 12 months.\n\nThis 3 hour workshop is designed for those retiring wit
	hin the year and covers the following topics:\n\nRetirement eligibility\n\
	nCompleting the UW retirement application\n\nRetiree medical plan choices 
	and enrollment\n\nApplying for Medicare\n\nLeave balances and VEBA\, if ap
	plicable\n\nNotifying your department about your separation\n\nWorking aft
	er retirement\n\nAccessibility Contact:  benefits@uw.edu Event Types: Lect
	ures/Seminars Event sponsors: UW Human Resources Benefits office More info
	:  ucs.admin.uw.edu…\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/live
	stream-retiring-from-the-uwrp-an-overview/17813210/2026-04-09T00
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/livestream-retiring-from-
	the-uwrp-an-overview/17813210/2026-04-09T00
LOCATION:University of Washington\, Seattle\, WA
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
END:VEVENT
